            { "ITM_BOK_Info_0200_1", "<PF_ITM_BOK_Info_0200_1>" },
            { "ITM_BOK_Info_0200_2", "Don't let up! Use your party members to unload an unmerciful amount of damage on your foes and win the day." },
            { "ITM_BOK_Info_0201_1", "Landing a successful hit with a psych will summon a circular Beatdrop gauge. Attack with another character while this gauge is displayed to drop the beat and increase your team's Groove." },
            { "ITM_BOK_Info_0201_2", "Keep a look out for clothing abilities and Social Network skills that can increase your Groove faster." },
            { "ITM_BOK_Info_0202_1", "<PF_ITM_BOK_Info_0202_1>" },
            { "ITM_BOK_Info_0202_2", "When you dodge, your character is untouchable for a split second—a handy trick when you're about to get a face full of pain. Note that certain Social Network skills can extend your invulnerability." },
            { "ITM_BOK_Info_0203_1", "Some Noise may counterattack if you pelt them with Psychs. Watch out when an enemy tries this, as no amount of damage dealt can interrupt them." },
            { "ITM_BOK_Info_0203_2", "You'll know an enemy is going to counter when they glow red. When you see that telltale sign, stop attacking and get ready to dodge." },
            { "ITM_BOK_Info_0204_1", "Enemies have elemental weaknesses that can be exploited for major damage. Keep in mind the elemental affinity of the pins you're wearing so you can pound your foes into submission." },
            { "ITM_BOK_Info_0204_2", "Here are the elements you'll find: Fire, Ice, Electric, Wind, Water, Stone, Poison, Burst, Sound, Light, Darkness, Gravity, Kinesis, and Time." },
            { "ITM_BOK_Info_0205_1", "Certain attacks can cast temporary status ailments on teammates or foes. These effects fade with time and range from slowly draining HP to immobilization." },
            { "ITM_BOK_Info_0205_2", "Some ailments—such as poisoned, shocked, and burning—drain HP, while others immobilize a character or enemy, such as stunned, chained, frozen, and entombed. Don't forget: certain items can cure (and prevent) what ails you!" },
            { "ITM_BOK_Info_0206_1", "You'll earn EXP and PP for every enemy defeated. EXP will raise your teammates' levels, while PP will raise the levels of the pins you used in combat." },
            { "ITM_BOK_Info_0206_2", "Here's how to increase PP earned: 1) wrack up multiple wins in a chain battle, 2) wrap up the fight quickly, and 3) don't take too much damage!" },
            { "ITM_BOK_Info_0207_1", "Launching an enemy back or into the air will make them unable to act, giving your team the perfect opportunity to show them a world of pain." },
            { "ITM_BOK_Info_0207_2", "Some enemies can't be knocked back or launched into the air, so make sure you have a back-up plan to roll with the punches." },
            { "ITM_BOK_Info_0208_1", "Increase your Groove to 200% or more to unleash super-charged Mashup attacks." },
            { "ITM_BOK_Info_0208_2", "Mashup attacks change depending on the element of the last Psych used in your combo. You can really power up the Mashup by using more characters in your combo." },
            { "ITM_BOK_Info_0209_1", "When your Groove's at 300%, you can unleash Killer Remixes as a team. The more teammates used to increase your Groove, the longer and more powerful your team attack will be." },
            { "ITM_BOK_Info_0209_2", "After using Killer Remixes, your team will recover HP. The more teammates used to unleash the attack, the more HP you'll recover." },
            { "ITM_BOK_Info_0211_1", "Enemies will occasionally leave behind pins after you defeat them. Pins received through battle vary depending on combat difficulty, the variety of Noise, and how high your drop rate is." },
            { "ITM_BOK_Info_0211_2", "You can increase the drop rate by winning more chain battles, and setting your level lower. To earn the really rare stuff, slash your level and take on chain battles!" },
            { "ITM_BOK_Info_0212_1", "Some pins can be evolved once they level up, while others must first meet certain requirements. Looking to collect every pin? Better start evolving them!" },
            { "ITM_BOK_Info_0212_2", "It's up to you whether or not to evolve a pin. Keeping your pins as-is and leveling them up is a totally viable strategy!" },
            { "ITM_BOK_Info_0213_1", "Certain pins, when worn together, can produce interesting effects." },
            { "ITM_BOK_Info_0213_2", "Read up on a pin in the pin menu to find out if it's capable of something extra special when worn with the right set." },
            { "ITM_BOK_Info_0214_1", "Uber Pins are extremely powerful—you guessed it—pins that can't be equipped without unlocking a unique skill on your Social Network." },
            { "ITM_BOK_Info_0214_2", "The more of these skills you unlock, the more Uber Pins you'll be able to equip." },
            { "ITM_BOK_Info_0215_1", "Looking to fill out your pin collection? Be aware that some can only be obtained through shops, battles, events, or by evolving them." },
            { "ITM_BOK_Info_0215_2", "To see which enemies drop which pins, check out the Noisepedia." },
            { "ITM_BOK_Info_0216_1", "<PF_ITM_BOK_Info_0216_1>" },
            { "ITM_BOK_Info_0216_2", "Certain skills in your Social Network can increase the total number of sets available to you." },
            { "ITM_BOK_Info_0217_1", "<PF_ITM_BOK_Info_0217_1>" },
            { "ITM_BOK_Info_0217_2", "Watch out for Noise symbols, though. Coming into contact with one will initiate combat." },
            { "ITM_BOK_Info_0218_1", "The Noise symbol you encounter dictates the main type of enemy you'll fight, which can be a handy feature when you're looking to take down a certain variety of foe." },
            { "ITM_BOK_Info_0218_2", "Want those Noise symbols to stay away? Some clothing items may contain the ability to keep them at bay." },
            { "ITM_BOK_Info_0219_1", "<PF_ITM_BOK_Info_0219_1>" },
            { "ITM_BOK_Info_0219_2", "If you're itching for chain battles, use Noise Magnet to draw Noise symbols to you. There's a fixed number of chain battles you can initiate, but certain Social Network skills can increase that number." },
            { "ITM_BOK_Info_0220_1", "Red Noise symbols contain weaker monsters, but don't let your guard down. Even red symbols can hide some fearsome foes." },
            { "ITM_BOK_Info_0220_2", "These symbols, unlike others, will reappear when you return to the location you fought them in." },
            { "ITM_BOK_Info_0221_1", "Blue Noise symbols contain tougher enemies than the ones you'll find in red symbols." },
            { "ITM_BOK_Info_0221_2", "You'll have to unlock skills on your Social Network in order to encounter these special symbols." },
            { "ITM_BOK_Info_0222_1", "Pink Noise symbols contain Pig Noise, which—if defeated—are guaranteed to drop pins." },
            { "ITM_BOK_Info_0222_2", "If you hear something oinking while scanning, that means Pig Noise is somewhere nearby." },
            { "ITM_BOK_Info_0223_1", "Some Pig Noise are immune to certain Psychs, so strategy is key. Try out a variety of Psychs to make these porkers rue the day they crossed you." },
            { "ITM_BOK_Info_0223_2", "Fighting these pigs comes with a time limit, but some articles of clothing have the ability to extend the timer." },
            { "ITM_BOK_Info_0224_1", "These rare, mysterious Noise symbols will run away if they spot Rindo and co." },
            { "ITM_BOK_Info_0224_2", "Defeating this rare type of Noise increases your drop rate, so if you want to score a ton of pins, try chaining them with other symbols." },
            { "ITM_BOK_Info_0225_1", "Orange Noise symbols only appear during Scramble Slams and, when defeated, will provide your team with Scramble Points." },
            { "ITM_BOK_Info_0225_2", "When facing off against this type of Noise, all other foes in the fight will drop Scramble Points, too. Score a heaping helping of points by chaining battles!" },
            { "ITM_BOK_Info_0226_1", "You'll be awarded one of three scores—gold, silver, or bronze—based on how fast you complete a dive. The better your score, the more FP you'll receive." },
            { "ITM_BOK_Info_0226_2", "To complete dives faster, try increasing your teammates' levels, eating different food, and equipping new badges and clothes." },
            { "ITM_BOK_Info_0227_1", "The red Noise found in dive battles are pissed off." },
            { "ITM_BOK_Info_0227_2", "Enraged Noise pack a serious punch and can be dangerous adversaries. Careful not to let them hit you!" },
            { "ITM_BOK_Info_0228_1", "The blue Noise found in dives are rather unhappy." },
            { "ITM_BOK_Info_0228_2", "Your team's HP will steadily drain while unhappy Noise is present, and the more there are, the more HP you'll bleed! Defeat these melancholy monsters first." },
            { "ITM_BOK_Info_0229_1", "The green Noise encountered in dive battles are at peace." },
            { "ITM_BOK_Info_0229_2", "Defeating this serene Noise will restore your team's HP." },
            { "ITM_BOK_Info_0230_1", "The purple Noise seen in dive battles are afraid." },
            { "ITM_BOK_Info_0230_2", "Fearful Noise are massive in size and unfazed by the attacks you throw at them. They also have a habit of countering, so know when to ease up!" },
            { "ITM_BOK_Info_0231_1", "Sell unwanted pins to earn ShibuPay, a form of digital currency used in the area." },
            { "ITM_BOK_Info_0231_2", "The Social Network skill ShibuPay Autoload can instantly convert money pins into ShibuPay currency, sparing you the hassle of selling them." },
            { "ITM_BOK_Info_0232_1", "<PF_ITM_BOK_Info_0232_1>" },
            { "ITM_BOK_Info_0232_2", "Some abilities only work if they're worn by certain characters. This specialty apparel is often more useful than standard clothing items." },
            { "ITM_BOK_Info_0233_1", "Clothing abilities won't activate unless your character's Style is greater than or equal to that of the garment. To increase your Style, try eating certain foods." },
            { "ITM_BOK_Info_0233_2", "There are a variety of clothing abilities available to you—some for combat, some for exploring the town, and some for rather peculiar purposes." },
            { "ITM_BOK_Info_0234_1", "Shops selling an item with the word <MK_11>Trade<MK_11> on it can't be purchased. Instead, you must—surprise, surprise!—trade in the corresponding Quest materials to obtain it." },
            { "ITM_BOK_Info_0234_2", "If the word <MK_11>Trade<MK_11> is grayed out, you don't have enough materials to acquire the item. Hit the streets to collect more of what you need." },
            { "ITM_BOK_Info_0235_1", "Continue to purchase from the same shop, and the employees will take a shine to you. Not only will they be nicer, they might even sell you special wares!" },
            { "ITM_BOK_Info_0235_2", "You can increase your VIP Rank with brand-name shops by wearing their clothes and pins into battle. The store's employees'll be glad for the free promotion!" },
            { "ITM_BOK_Info_0236_1", "You can increase your team's stats by eating food... The end. Seriously, it's that easy to boost your stats." },
            { "ITM_BOK_Info_0236_2", "You won't be able to eat any more once you're full, but battles can make you hungry again. Eat, fight, get hungry. Rinse and repeat. Your team'll be happier for it!" },
            { "ITM_BOK_Info_0237_1", "Each of your characters has a favorite snack, and by eating it, they'll receive a bonus stat boost." },
            { "ITM_BOK_Info_0237_2", "Want to know what kind of food a character likes? Watch how they react when they eat something. They're not exactly coy about their preferences..." },
            { "ITM_BOK_Info_0238_1", "The art in the Udagawa Backstreets is a reflection of the wall you've tagged in the Graffiti section of the Records menu. Sounds like a good chance to spice up Shibuya with your own personal style!" },
            { "ITM_BOK_Info_0238_2", "Obtain new graffiti by helping out around town. For hints on how to obtain each piece of street art, check out the Graffiti section of the Records menu." },
            { "ITM_BOK_Info_0239_1", "During a Scramble Slam battle, an enemy marked with the word <MK_11>Bonus<MK_11> will appear. Take them down to earn your team a boat load of points." },
            { "ITM_BOK_Info_0239_2", "Unload combos on enemies to earn more Scramble Points. Also, try to save the Bonus for last to really come away from a fight flushed with points." },
            { "ITM_BOK_Info_0240_1", "<PF_ITM_BOK_Info_0240_1>" },
            { "ITM_BOK_Info_0240_2", "Open up these notes anytime, even when you're in the middle of solving a real head-scratcher of a puzzle. They might just have the answers!" },
            { "ITM_BOK_Info_0241_1", "From the Thoughts tab of the main menu, use FP to unlock skills on your characters' Social Network." },
            { "ITM_BOK_Info_0241_2", "Advance the story, solve problems around town, and befriend shop employees to grow your Social Network!" },
            { "ITM_BOK_Info_0242_1", "Some events in town have no bearing on the main story, meaning you can ignore them. However, these interludes offer FP and items, so it's in your interest to be philanthropic." },
            { "ITM_BOK_Info_0242_2", "Want to see if you have any past unresolved side quests? Check the Chapter screen in the Records menu." },
            { "ITM_BOK_Info_0243_1", "From the Chapter screen in the Records menu, you can return to any day you've already completed. This is a handy trick if you missed something important or need to strengthen your team." },
            { "ITM_BOK_Info_0243_2", "You'll retain all current items, party members, and stats when you jump back in time, which will make clearing skipped missions or besting undefeated enemies easier." },
            { "ITM_MSC_Info_0001", "<MK_11>Wander Around Shibuya<MK_11><BR>Get into the groove for your newest adventure. As the tune ramps up, so will your excitement." },
            { "ITM_MSC_Info_0002", "<MK_11>INCONGRUOUS<MK_11><BR>Who needs harmony, anyway? Break free from the confines of musical standards with this unpredictable jam." },
            { "ITM_MSC_Info_0003", "<MK_11>Your Ocean<MK_11><BR>Listless vocals over a hard guitar riff make a solid track for the new generation." },
            { "ITM_MSC_Info_0004", "<MK_11>Insomnia<MK_11><BR>Just listening to these synth beats makes you feel like you can uncover all of the city's secrets." },
            { "ITM_MSC_Info_0005", "<MK_11>Breaking Free<MK_11><BR>The melodious vocals of this rock number give just the push you need to break through all obstacles standing in your way." },
            { "ITM_MSC_Info_0006", "<MK_11>Hustle and Bustle<MK_11><BR>This cute, electro-pop bop will keep you grounded and remind you of exactly where you are." },
            { "ITM_MSC_Info_0007", "<MK_11>Shibuya Survivor<MK_11><BR>Relaxed vocals meticulously mesh with deep guitar tones to give this track a weighty, underground feel." },
            { "ITM_MSC_Info_0008", "<MK_11>Kill the Itch<MK_11><BR>A proper rock jam, this song will swing its way into your head as you plow through life's adversities." },
            { "ITM_MSC_Info_0009", "<MK_11>unconscious<MK_11><BR>Nothing lasts in this world, but this song makes you feel like there's something you've missed lurking just out of sight." },
            { "ITM_MSC_Info_0010", "<MK_11>Rockin' Rockin'<MK_11><BR>Feel the beat pulse from the very ground beneath you as you rock out to this killer track. Don't be surprised if everyone else joins in, too." },
            { "ITM_MSC_Info_0011", "<MK_11>Unpainted<MK_11><BR>Lose yourself in these beats and forget all about the pain that fills your sorrowed heart." },
            { "ITM_MSC_Info_0012", "<MK_11>DIVIDE<MK_11><BR>This emotional jam may be just what you need to draw up and reconcile the conflicting truths at your core." },
            { "ITM_MSC_Info_0013", "<MK_11>We’re Losing You<MK_11><BR>Black or white? Silence won't stand. The hardcore sound of this song penetrates your heart and resonates with the Noise within." },
            { "ITM_MSC_Info_0014", "<MK_11>LAST CALL<MK_11><BR>Quick, ambient beats summon forth the unexpected with pleasant, straight-shooting vocals." },
            { "ITM_MSC_Info_0015", "<MK_11>Storm<MK_11><BR>If you aren't careful, the funky flow of this knock-out track may sweep you away." },
            { "ITM_MSC_Info_0016", "<MK_11>The Beginning of a Happy Life<MK_11><BR>Bold synth lines and pronounced bass slaps will keep you on-beat as you step out into a new day." },
            { "ITM_MSC_Info_0017", "<MK_11>CHASE<MK_11><BR>Never look back. These intense acoustic beats will carry you forward into a shining new era." },
            { "ITM_MSC_Info_0018", "<MK_11>bird in the hand<MK_11><BR>Conflicting vocals never quite find common ground in this deceptively simple number." },
            { "ITM_MSC_Info_0019", "<MK_11>Beyond Oblivion<MK_11><BR>Friendship becomes memory, and memory becomes a dream. This is an elegy for all the grieving hearts out there." },
            { "ITM_MSC_Info_0020", "<MK_11>World Is Yours<MK_11><BR>Melodies rise from the ashes as the beat heats up in this homage track." },
            { "ITM_MSC_Info_0021", "<MK_11>take away<MK_11><BR>You just can't resist that smile, can you? You know the one. Don't forget to top up ShibuPay before you go." },
            { "ITM_MSC_Info_0022", "<MK_11>NEW GAME<MK_11><BR>The world ends with this hard rock anthem. There's no stopping the countdown now." },
            { "ITM_MSC_Info_0023", "<MK_11>LITTLE THINGS - JP<MK_11><BR>Soothing piano tones and persistent percussion envelop you like the sunlight streaming over the crossing." },
            { "ITM_MSC_Info_0024", "<MK_11>hopeless<MK_11><BR>There is not a single ray of light to guide you through despair. Only a melancholic nocturne to accompany you in sorrow." },
            { "ITM_MSC_Info_0025", "<MK_11>disturbance<MK_11><BR>Apprehension. Fear. Dread. Your hair stands on end as you listen to this capriccio of horrors to come." },
            { "ITM_MSC_Info_0026", "<MK_11>death throes<MK_11><BR>Danger draws ever nearer. Will you persevere? Or will you succumb to the perils that await?" },
            { "ITM_MSC_Info_0027", "<MK_11>a tranquil mind<MK_11><BR>Relax. Take a deep breath. Let the aria soothe you and clear your troubled mind." },
            { "ITM_MSC_Info_0028", "<MK_11>act the fool<MK_11><BR>You've got a funny feeling. Something's coming, and you've got a hunch about what it is." },
            { "ITM_MSC_Info_0029", "<MK_11>ENCOUNTER<MK_11><BR>You've got a lock on your prey. Now is the time to strike while your anticipation is hightened by this toccata." },
            { "ITM_MSC_Info_0030", "<MK_11>peaceful day<MK_11><BR>When you hear this chipper number, you know the day is won. Time to kick back and enjoy some hard-earned down time." },
            { "ITM_MSC_Info_0031", "<MK_11>Twister (NEO Mix)<MK_11><BR>The masterpiece returns, bestowing upon its listeners a burst of musical adrenaline. <MK_11>That power is yet unknown.<MK_11>" },
            { "ITM_MSC_Info_0032", "<MK_11>Revelation (NEO Mix)<MK_11><BR>Synthesizers heighten the senses as powerful vocals remind you of what came before. It's time to face new challenges with old friends." },
            { "ITM_MSC_Info_0033", "<MK_11>March On (NEO Mix)<MK_11><BR>Hot-and-cold vocals over dystopian shouts set this pop bop apart from the crowd." },
            { "ITM_MSC_Info_0034", "<MK_11>Calling (NEO Mix)<MK_11><BR>This tune is a sure sign that something serious is about to go down. It beckons you, <MK_11>dear friend, once more<MK_11>." },
            { "ITM_MSC_Info_0035", "<MK_11>Hybrid (NEO Mix)<MK_11><BR>Sprint through the danger zone as this jam dashes from perilous to chill and back again." },
            { "ITM_MSC_Info_0036", "<MK_11>Ooparts - JP (NEO Mix)<MK_11><BR>Dissonance defines this timeless tune for every generation, with conflicting genres representing clashing viewpoints." },
            { "ITM_MSC_Info_0037", "<MK_11>Jump Over Yourself (NEO Mix)<MK_11><BR>An unforgettable intro gives way to feelings of restraint and uncertainty. But never fear. The answers are waiting for you to look back to them." },
            { "ITM_MSC_Info_0038", "<MK_11>Someday - JP (NEO Mix)<MK_11><BR>This one's a classic! The tried-and-true hard rock tune really takes you back." },
            { "ITM_MSC_Info_0039", "<MK_11>Make or Break (NEO Mix)<MK_11><BR>You'll be singing along with this synth-and-drum number in no time. It's just too catchy to resist." },
            { "ITM_MSC_Info_0040", "<MK_11>SCRAMBLE<MK_11><BR>It starts out tame, but quickly climbs up to energetic heights. Throw in some orthodox pop elements, and you've got a sure earworm." },
            { "ITM_MSC_Info_0041", "<MK_11>Revelation - JP (NEO Mix)<MK_11><BR>Steady vocals lay on the melodic drama. Listening to this, you feel like not even fate can get in your way." },
            { "ITM_MSC_Info_0042", "<MK_11>Transformation (NEO Mix)<MK_11><BR>When there's no telling what will unfold, a dramatic orchestral arrangement gives you the courage to roll the dice." },
            { "ITM_MSC_Info_0043", "<MK_11>Three Minutes Clapping (NEO Mix)<MK_11><BR>A funky beat and cheering crowds make this jam the perfect pick-me-up when you need some encouragement before ripping through Noise." },
            { "ITM_MSC_Info_0044", "<MK_11>The One Star (NEO Mix)<MK_11><BR>A solid jam with a nifty guitar riff. You'll want to put on some nice headphones for this one." },
            { "ITM_MSC_Info_0045", "<MK_11>OWARI-HAJIMARI (NEO Mix)<MK_11><BR>Crank up the volume, 'cause this genre-defying piece is best enjoyed loud." },
            { "ITM_MSC_Info_0046", "<MK_11>OWARI-HAJIMARI - JP (NEO Mix)<MK_11><BR>Crank up the volume, 'cause this genre-defying piece is best enjoyed loud." },
            { "ITM_MSC_Info_0047", "<MK_11>Twister<MK_11><BR>It's back in all its original glory. All jam and no frills, it'll have you feeling fresh as ever." },
            { "ITM_MSC_Info_0048", "<MK_11>Someday (NEO Mix)<MK_11><BR>This one's a classic! The tried-and-true hard rock tune really gets you pumped up." },
            { "ITM_MSC_Info_0049", "<MK_11>Hybrid - JP (NEO Mix)<MK_11><BR>Sprint through the danger zone as this jam dashes from perilous to chill and back again, this time in Japanese." },
            { "ITM_MSC_Info_0050", "<MK_11>Rockin' Rockin' (Live Version)<MK_11><BR>The legendary act has taken the stage once more! Bask in the sweet storm that is their quintessential sound, and remember: this dream ends with you." },
            { "ITM_MSC_Info_0051", "<MK_11>LITTLE THINGS<MK_11><BR>Once again, the world begins with you, standing in the crossing amid infinite possibilities—but only the ones you can perceive will help you change fate." },
            { "ITM_FOD_Info_9999", "Food Info" },
            { "ITM_FOD_Info_0000", "A cup of coffee made from lightly-roasted beans with a fresh, fruity aroma. Cold pressed to reduce bitterness, this blend washes over you like a summer breeze.<BR>*Amount of ice subject to change" },
            { "ITM_FOD_Info_0001", "A cup of cold brew blended with low-calorie, lowfat milk that adds a rich smoothness without detracting from the coffee's natural aroma.<BR>*Milk-to-coffee ratio subject to change" },
            { "ITM_FOD_Info_0002", "This café staple tastes as refreshing as it looks. You <i>could</i> eat the ice cream first, but then it's just a melon soda with a cherry, and where's the fun in that?<BR>*Size of scoop subject to change" },
            { "ITM_FOD_Info_0003", "A cup of joe brewed from a unique blend of beans from Central and South America. Praised by coffee aficionados for its light mouthfeel and rich aftertaste.<BR>*Specific blend subject to change" },
            { "ITM_FOD_Info_0004", "A café staple that blends espresso coffee with warm milk—what's not to love? Slightly less milk than other places, perhaps, but Hachiko believes that bitter is better.<BR>*Stencil art subject to change" },
            { "ITM_FOD_Info_0005", "A sweet treat baked fresh in-house before opening. Bursting with bitter chocolate, this confection crumbles in your mouth and goes perfectly with a hot cup of joe.<BR>*Number of chunks subject to change" },
            { "ITM_FOD_Info_0006", "A popular menu item that combines three perennial favorites: bacon, lettuce, and tomato. Bacon is lightly fried just before assembly for extra aroma.<BR>*Inclusion of tomato subject to change" },
            { "ITM_FOD_Info_0007", "A savory dessert that nestles fresh strawberry, kiwi, and orange among waves of whipped cream and crams it all between two slices of bread. Quite photogenic.<BR>*Amount of cream subject to change" },
            { "ITM_FOD_Info_0008", "A Sapporo specialty made from a hybrid of pork-and-chicken stock and a bonito-infused seafood soup. Add some chicken, a hearty helping of veggies, and a panoply of spices, and you've got yourself a meal!<BR>*Level of heat subject to change" },
            { "ITM_FOD_Info_0100", "A menu mainstay since the franchise's establishment, this ground beef patty is grilled to perfection and sandwiched between two natural yeast buns alongside farm-fresh organic veggies." },
            { "ITM_FOD_Info_0101", "This burger isn't a champion in name only: it's also JB's most popular menu item—and with good reason. Featuring two patties and extra cheese, this sandwich is a hungry meat-lover's dream." },
            { "ITM_FOD_Info_0102", "This sandwich features a freshly-fried pollock fillet smothered in a refreshingly tart homemade tartar sauce. Hardcore JB fans note the acidity of the lemon and pickles are what truly tie this dish together." },
            { "ITM_FOD_Info_0103", "An extra-special wagyu sandwich created in commemoration of the franchise's 30th anniversary that now enjoys a permanent spot on the menu. Can <i>you</i> conquer this behemoth burger?" },
            { "ITM_FOD_Info_0104", "These delectable sticks are cut from unskinned potatoes and fried twice—first at a low temperature, then high—to give them that irresistible <MK_11>crunchy on the outside, soft on the inside<MK_11> texture." },
            { "ITM_FOD_Info_0105", "This super-carbonated soft drink is the perfect complement to any Justice Burger sandwich. The extra fizz is sure to shock your system and set your mouth atingle!" },
            { "ITM_FOD_Info_0106", "More sweet than sour, this soft drink pairs surprisingly well with the menu's meatier items. Made with 100% real juice, squeezed from real oranges grown on real farms! (Really!)" },
            { "ITM_FOD_Info_0200", "Served in a flavorful white sesame soup, this dish's combination of spicy chili oil and Japanese pepper help bring out the gentle flavor of its true star: black pepper. One for true ramen enthusiasts." },
            { "ITM_FOD_Info_0201", "The thickest noodles in town served in a pork-bone broth alongside chunky slices of roasted pork fillet and plenty of pork fat for good measure. Contains an adult male's recommended daily calorie intake and then some! Truly, the guiltiest of pleasures." },
            { "ITM_FOD_Info_0202", "An original recipe unique to G4G that combines two different types of oil noodle dishes. Savor the taste of ultra-thick noodles coated in a secret sauce that's been passed down through the generations." },
            { "ITM_FOD_Info_0203", "An alternative take on the G4G standard, this dish features a rich black sesame soup that you won't soon forget. The minced pork is marinated in a spicy blend of garlic, ginger, and pepper to give it a satisfying kick." },
            { "ITM_FOD_Info_0300", "The symbol of SBY BBQ, this piglet is roasted to perfection, from its crispy skin to its sweet and succulent meat. Served atop a bed of veggies, this dish is sure to leave a tasty impression!" },
            { "ITM_FOD_Info_0301", "This free-range chicken goes into a custom-made roaster and comes out practically brimming with juice. Best enjoyed in sandwich form, topped with SBY BBQ's homemade relish and cole slaw." },
            { "ITM_FOD_Info_0302", "A Brazilian barbecue dish comprised of picanha steak, grilled rare and topped with a molho vinaigrette. (The chef doing the slicing and serving is quite the visual feast as well!)" },
            { "ITM_FOD_Info_0303", "This meat is aged in a freezer for a full month, then roasted on high heat to create a memorable dish with a nutty aroma and a rich flavor. Diners hoping to savor the Chateaubriand should note reservations can only be booked a year in advance." },
            { "ITM_FOD_Info_0304", "A popular menu item that's sure to make a splash on social media. Don't let its appearance fool you: this oven-roasted head is more edible than you think, especially the meaty cheeks and the collagen-rich eye sockets!" },
            { "ITM_FOD_Info_0305", "Sourced directly from Australia, this roasted critter is rich in protein and low in calories. Some liken its texture to chicken, but true enthusiasts know nothing compares to freshly grilled 'gator." },
            { "ITM_FOD_Info_0400", "A popular parfait featuring a selection of seasonal fruits. Served atop layers of custard and topped with a tasteful dollop of whipped cream so as to allow diners to enjoy the fruit's natural flavors." },
            { "ITM_FOD_Info_0401", "This decadent delight takes rich French chocolate ice cream and harmonizes it with a hazelnut whip. Bitter espresso jelly and subtly sour berry sauce on top combine to create a real treat for the refined palate." },
            { "ITM_FOD_Info_0402", "This parfait matches the fruity tartness of its ruby chocolate ice cream with a delightfully sour yogurt sauce, then tops it all off with a colorful cranberry drizzle. Destined to be the talk of Udagawa in no time!" },
            { "ITM_FOD_Info_0403", "A pretty parfait that tastes even better than it already looks. The chef encourages diners to start with the merengue on top and work their way down to the cassis sherbet below, but hey—it's your dessert. Eat it however you please!" },
            { "ITM_FOD_Info_0500", "A popular Taiwanese drink that blends a strong black tea with milk and tapioca pearls. These spongy <MK_11>bubbles<MK_11> are prepared from scratch every morning, giving them an unparalleled freshness." },
            { "ITM_FOD_Info_0501", "One of Bubblevision's most popular menu items, this drink doubles up on its flavor kick of green tea, mixing it in with the milk as well as kneading it into the tapioca pearls. What'll they think of next?" },
            { "ITM_FOD_Info_0502", "This creamy concoction combines rich Taiwanese tea with freshly blended strawberries and fruit-flavored tapioca pearls. A sweet treat that appeals to customers of all ages." },
            { "ITM_FOD_Info_0503", "The strong sweetness of Okinawan brown sugar pairs perfectly with the black tea base to create a complex flavor profile that rivals any finely crafted confection. Good to the very last pearl!" },
            { "ITM_FOD_Info_0504", "A decadent drink that balances the full-bodied sweetness of 100% real mango purée with the more austere taste of Taiwanese tea. It won't linger on your tongue, but it will have you craving another cup." },
            { "ITM_FOD_Info_0600", "Sample all three of the Don's famous curries with this single plate—perfect for the indecisive diner. Optionally topped with crispy cheese and roast pork, but just as tasty without." },
            { "ITM_FOD_Info_0601", "A spicy dish that infuses South Indian curry with a Japanese broth. Astute diners will detect aromatic notes of coriander and cumin, as well as a special dusting of cloves added at the chef's insistence." },
            { "ITM_FOD_Info_0602", "A rich-yet-healthy dish that combines three types of dal—mung, masur, and chana—with fragrant fried onions to create a curry that the Don's diners will savor down to the very last spoonful." },
            { "ITM_FOD_Info_0603", "This South Indian dish delivers two types of fresh mackerel in a curry that balances the tartness of tamarind and tomato against the mellow sweetness of coconut, with tempered curry leaf and mustard seed adding some extra aroma." },
            { "ITM_FOD_Info_0604", "This Japanese twist on the traditional Indian dish infuses a bowl of mixed rice with bonito broth and keema-style mussels and scallops. Mix in a variety of condiments to create a chain reaction of flavor—and don't forget the spicy miso soup on the side!" },
            { "ITM_FOD_Info_0700", "A convenience store staple known as one of Japan's most famous fast foods. This rice ball contains two plums for the price of one—the kind of deal only Moyai Mart can provide!" },
            { "ITM_FOD_Info_0701", "This rice ball is quite literally bursting with flakes of fragrant salmon, first preserved in salt, then air-dried to enhance the flavor. You won't get more yum for your yen anywhere else!" },
            { "ITM_FOD_Info_0702", "A cast of scrumptious sidekicks like fried prawn, scrambled egg, and stewed root veggies surround this lunch box's superstar: a grilled salmon fillet. Tasty enough to earn a standing ovation!" },
            { "ITM_FOD_Info_0703", "(Word to the wise: if it ain't fresh from the fryer, throw it back on the rack!)" },
            { "ITM_FOD_Info_0704", "This seasonal soup enjoys extreme popularity among Moyai Mart patrons. Some even throw in a plain onigiri to soak up the bonito-infused broth and enjoy it as a makeshift risotto-on-the-go." },
            { "ITM_FOD_Info_0705", "A bag of Hokkaido crisps, cut thick and fried to crunchy perfection. The <MK_11>best enjoyed by<MK_11> date isn't just a suggestion: Moyai Mart takes unsold bags off the shelves to ensure customers enjoy only the freshest snacks." },
            { "ITM_FOD_Info_0800", "A luxurious meal containing more marbled Matsuzaka beef than you could shake a stick at. Your tastebuds will delight the second this high-grade meat touches your tongue. Beef bowls don't get better than this." },
            { "ITM_FOD_Info_0801", "An unparalleled bowl practically overflowing with a selection of the fattiest tuna and other fine seafood, sourced fresh from Toyosu Fish Market every morning and expertly arranged by the head chef himself." },
            { "ITM_FOD_Info_0802", "A primo bowl featuring two of Hokkaido's finest delicacies: thick slices of creamy sea urchin, and delectable little globules of salmon roe. One bite of briny goodness will whisk you away to the isle up north." },
            { "ITM_FOD_Info_0803", "A meaty bowl filled with juicy slices of beef roasted to aromatic perfection. Served with a side of watercress and wasabi-infused sour cream to cleanse your palate and add some oomph to your <i>umami</i>." },
            { "ITM_FOD_Info_0804", "A popular bowl featuring eel prepared Nagoya-style: grilled, not steamed. Enjoy your first serving with sweet soy sauce, your second with wasabi and scallions, and your third with a splash of soup." },
            { "ITM_FOD_Info_0805", "A legendary bowl boasting an all-star lineup of nine varieties of meat assembled from all over Japan: beef, pork, chicken, mutton, duck, venison, boar, bear, and rabbit. A carnivore's dream come true!" },
            { "ITM_FOD_Info_0900", "A special bowl containing roughly 200% of your daily recommended intake of leafy greens. Drizzled with a homemade dressing tasty enough to entice even the veggie-averse." },
            { "ITM_FOD_Info_0901", "A piece of thick-cut bread slathered in a special-made mayo, toasted in the oven, then topped with a whole avocado so rich you won't believe it's not lard. (Really—it's not!)" },
            { "ITM_FOD_Info_0902", "A seasonal broth brimming with diced carrots, potatoes, and other root vegetables. This guilt-free bowl is low in calories, so feel free to eat your fill and then some." },
            { "ITM_FOD_Info_0903", "Spinach, kale, and other leafy greens are blended with apples, oranges, and a squirt of lemon juice to create this vitamin-rich power drink. An excellent breakfast substitute." },
            { "ITM_FOD_Info_0904", "This tasty treat blends a handful of super-nutritious açaí with some of its berry brethren and a splash of milk to create a drink that's rich in iron, polyphenols, and of course flavor." },
            { "ITM_FOD_Info_0905", "A taste of the Shibuya skies, sampled from 300 feet above the city and triple filtered for extra purity. Makes for a neat souvenir even though it's, y'know...just air." },
            { "ITM_FOD_Info_1000", "A popular Korean street food made of melty mozzarella cheese wrapped in a sweet corn coating. Top it with ketchup, mustard, maple syrup—whatever condiment calls to you!" },
            { "ITM_FOD_Info_1001", "This Korean dessert features a fried banana that melts in your mouth and pairs perfectly with a good chocolate drizzle. One viral blog post away from becoming a foodie phenom." },
            { "ITM_FOD_Info_1002", "These tiny dough balls are fried, then filled with bean paste and a sour soup to create a bite-sized treat that's fun to eat. Pop a couple pani puri, and it's party time!" },
            { "ITM_FOD_Info_1003", "This dim sum staple wraps minced pork into little dumplings, then steams them in a bamboo basket. Dine with caution, however: the savory soup inside might scald you!" },
            { "ITM_FOD_Info_1004", "Perhaps the most popular of Osaka's street foods, these octopus balls are crispy on the outside and gooey on the inside. Be sure to add some mayonnaise—it's just <i>better</i> here." },
            { "ITM_FOD_Info_1100", "A soft serve cone made with all-natural milk sent straight from the dairy. Its smooth mouthfeel and refreshing sweetness make it impossible to pass up." },
            { "ITM_FOD_Info_1101", "A seasonal crêpe filled with luxurious shine muscat grapes, then topped with a champagne-infused whipped cream for a little extra decadence. Cheers!" },
            { "ITM_FOD_Info_1102", "This popular crêpe is positively bursting with fruit. Strawberries, raspberries, and blueberries are gorgeously arranged atop a bed of rum-flavored whipped cream." },
            { "ITM_FOD_Info_1103", "This creamy treat boasts a bitter cacao flavor with a smooth aftertaste. With specially-selected cacao beans ground into the cone as well, this dessert is truly good to the last bite." },
            { "ITM_FOD_Info_1104", "Super-sweet satsuma potatoes are stone-roasted, then mashed up and blended into smooth, 100%-milk soft serve. Sprinkled with sugary fry bits because who doesn't like the bits!?" },
            { "ITM_FOD_Info_1200", "This meaty Mexican dish features seared steak diced up and wrapped in an all-corn tortilla. Astute eaters will detect a smoky flavor from the roasted tomato-and-onion salsa." },
            { "ITM_FOD_Info_1201", "A secret menu item reserved for regulars, this wrap is not for the untrained tongue. The brutal blend of habanero and ghost peppers salsa is so hot, you'll be crying out for <i>madre</i>." },
            { "ITM_FOD_Info_1202", "This meat-filled spinach tortilla is topped with chopped green chilies for a colorful dish that gives your tongue a refreshing tingle. Only available to returning customers." },
            { "ITM_FOD_Info_1203", "The cacao-rich mole sauce and its exquisite blend of cinnamon, cloves, and other spices serve as perfect complements to the grilled chicken in this lavish dish. If you spot this on the lunch menu, consider yourself lucky!" },
            { "ITM_FOD_Info_1300", "Suzu's chef starts with a simmered-chicken stock, then finishes by stirring in a harmonious blend of tamari and soy sauce—the perfect bath for some slightly-crimped noodles." },
            { "ITM_FOD_Info_1301", "Don't let the translucent broth fool you: it's full of flavor, thanks to the unique combination of chicken, scallops, kelp, and five types of salt. The lively lemon accent is sure to brighten your day." },
            { "ITM_FOD_Info_1302", "Light on the palate but heavy on flavor, this bowl is one of Suzu's best. An extra bit of miso is caramelized and drizzled over the noodles just before serving for a smoky touch." },
            { "ITM_FOD_Info_1303", "This bowl's namesake provides a smooth spiciness and a subtly savory flavor. Add some scallions and a dash of sesame oil, and you've got a dish that's sure to have you coming back for more." },
            { "ITM_FOD_Info_1400", "The scent and sweetness of citrus give this dimbula tea a clean and refreshing finish. Enjoy the orange slices after your drink for an extra dose of vitamin C!" },
            { "ITM_FOD_Info_1401", "A fruity tea drink that's honestly more fruit than tea. Perfectly preserved strawberries, raspberries, and blueberries harmonizes to create a drink good enough to call <MK_11>dessert.<MK_11>" },
            { "ITM_FOD_Info_1402", "A refreshing soda drink that hits the spot on a sweltering hot day. Throw in a few zesty lemon slices to stay extra cool for the summer!" },
            { "ITM_FOD_Info_1403", "A delicious soda drink with a gorgeous rouge color. The secret to bringing out the berries' juicy sweetness is a dash of strawberry vinegar—just don't tell anyone!" },
            { "ITM_FOD_Info_1500", "This North Indian platter features chicken, mutton, and other meaty curries alongside both naan and roti. Nuts and cream also play a role in enriching these dishes." },
            { "ITM_FOD_Info_1501", "This South Indian platter highlights vegetarian sambar and the hot-and-sour rasam, serving them with rice. Mix in the sides or enjoy them separately—it's up to you!" },
            { "ITM_FOD_Info_1502", "This North Indian platter caters to non-carnivorous folks by providing an unbelievably savory meal that won't leave you feeling overly full afterward." },
            { "ITM_FOD_Info_1503", "An Indian crêpe-like snack made from a fermented batter of rice and lentils, stuffed with spicy potatoes, and then served with sambar and chutney." },
            { "ITM_FOD_Info_1504", "An Indian rice dish featuring layers of basmati rice and chicken gravy cooked together in a special oven. Often mixed and enjoyed with raita, but totally tasty on its own as well." },
            { "ITM_FOD_Info_1600", "This fish-shaped snack bears no gustatory resemblance to the seabream after which it's modeled. Choose red bean filling for a sweet treat, or cheese for a savory snack." },
            { "ITM_FOD_Info_1601", "Gently boiled Hokkaido azuki beans and springy spheres of mochi decorate this delectable dish featuring soft serve drizzled with a thick matcha sauce." },
            { "ITM_FOD_Info_1602", "This decadent dessert builds upon its predecessor by adding green tea-flavored ice cream and bavarois, creating a multi-dimensional matcha experience that will have other diners green with envy." },
            { "ITM_FOD_Info_1603", "These exquisite balls of mochi are topped with a rich red bean paste nearly twenty years in the making. The impeccable balance of sweet and savory is impossible to beat." },
            { "ITM_FOD_Info_1604", "This delightfully colorful dessert was added to the menu after the founder visited Sendai. The edamame are ground by hand to preserve the proper flavor and texture." },
            { "ITM_FOD_Info_1700", "Dripping with a rich cashew cream, these super-soft soufflé-cakes melt in your mouth. Served with a variety of fruits to make this pleasure feel a little less guilty." },
            { "ITM_FOD_Info_1701", "A lightly sweetened frozen treat that's fluffier than you might expect. The tangy strawberry sauce complements the condensed milk and sets diners' hearts aflutter." },
            { "ITM_FOD_Info_1702", "Milky mint-flavored ice is shaved into a fine powder, then mixed with crushed mint and drizzled with a rich bitter chocolate sauce for a sweet treat perfect for a hot summer day." },
            { "ITM_FOD_Info_1703", "A stack of fluffy soufflé-cakes covered in chocolate cream. Lighter on sweetness and lower in calories than they would appear, so don't hesitate to order a second plate!" },
            { "ITM_FOD_Info_1704", "This frozen treat celebrates the full-bodied sweetness of ripe mango by utilizing the tropical fruit in every element of the dish, from the ice on the bottom to the whip on top." },
