            { "PF_PS4_ITM_BDG_Info_0288", "Draw in <CRE>3</C> objects at random, then use the Left Stick to roll it around and deal damage. Enemies will be <CRE>sent flying</C> on impact. Engraved with the words, <MK_11>Magnetic dipoles are the way of the world.<MK_11>" },
            { "PF_PS4_ITM_BDG_Info_0302", "Hold and release the button to close in on your target and assail them with your fists, then finish with a hard hit that <CRE>knocks the enemy back</C>. Hold longer to throw more punches. Engraved with the words, <MK_11>A true friend shares your dreams.<MK_11>" },
            { "PF_PS4_ITM_BDG_Info_0312", "Draw in building debris, then use the Left Stick to roll it around and deal damage. Enemies will be <CRE>sent flying</C> on impact." },
            { "PF_PS4_ITM_BOK_Info_0200_1", "Control multiple characters in combat by pressing their designated buttons to unleash a myriad of attacks." },
            { "PF_PS4_ITM_BOK_Info_0202_1", "You can dodge an enemy's attack by pressing the × Button. Learn your foes' attack patterns to get a feel for when you need to evade." },
            { "PF_PS4_ITM_BOK_Info_0216_1", "Press the Touch Pad Button on the Pins menu to switch decks. Assemble a variety of pin sets, then swap between them to suit the occasion." },
            { "PF_PS4_ITM_BOK_Info_0217_1", "Hit the R1 Button to scan an area and peer into people's thoughts." },
            { "PF_PS4_ITM_BOK_Info_0219_1", "Once you touch a Noise symbol, either wait for the battle to begin automatically or press the <PS_button_circle> Button. Touch more Noise symbols before combat begins to create chain battles." },
            { "PF_PS4_ITM_BOK_Info_0232_1", "Hit the OPTIONS Button on the Threads menu to see the abilities you've unlocked on your equipped garments." },
            { "PF_PS4_ITM_BOK_Info_0240_1", "Press the L1 Button outside of combat to see what kind of information you've gleaned during your adventure. These notes are especially useful when you're unsure what to do next." },
            { "PF_PS4_SKL_Info_0009", "Press the × Button after you're sent flying by an attack to immediately regain your footing." },
            { "PF_PS4_SKL_Info_0013", "Hold the R2 Button while scanning to draw in nearby Noise." },
            { "PF_PS4_SKL_Info_0014", "Hold the R2 Button while scanning to draw in Noise from even further away." },
            { "PF_PS4_SKL_Info_0027", "Allows you to equip an extra pin assigned to the same button as another." },
            { "PF_PS4_SKL_Info_0036", "Press the <PS_button_circle> Button to jump over certain walls and fences." },
            { "PF_PS4_TIPS_01_U", "Tilt the Left Stick to move." },
            { "PF_PS4_TIPS_02_U", "Press the R1 Button to scan your surroundings." },
            { "PF_PS4_TIPS_03_U", "Press the R1 Button to scan your surroundings." },
            { "PF_PS4_TIPS_03_D", "Scanning also allows you to hear people's thoughts. <CYE>Press the <PS_button_circle> Button</C> near one of these pensive persons to get an even clearer idea of what's on their mind." },
            { "PF_PS4_TIPS_04_D", "Rindo and the gang can tap into their latent psychic powers using the <CYE>pins</C> they've equipped. <CAQ>Press the button assigned to a given pin</C> to unleash its corresponding psych." },
            { "PF_PS4_TIPS_05_D", "Tilt the Left Stick to <CAQ>move</C> the character you last used. <CAQ>Target foes</C> by tilting the Right Stick, and <CAQ>evade their attacks</C> by pressing the × Button." },
            { "PF_PS4_TIPS_08_D", "Press the 〇 Button when your <CYE>Groove is at 100%</C> to unleash a <CYE>Mashup</C> and blast your foes with a super-powerful combo psych." },
            { "PF_PS4_TIPS_09_D", "Press the 〇 Button when your Groove is at 300% and your team will unite to unleash a devastating psych assault known as a <CYE>Killer Remix</C>. Tilt the Left Stick to target enemies, and press the 〇 Button to let 'em have it!" },
            { "PF_PS4_TIPS_10_U", "Use L1 or R1 Buttons to access the <CAQ>Pins</C> tab of the main menu, where you can adjust your party members' pin loadouts." },
            { "PF_PS4_TIPS_11_U", "Use the L1 or R1 Buttons to access the <CAQ>Threads</C> tab of the main menu, where you can dress your party members with a variety of clothing and accessories." },
            { "PF_PS4_TIPS_12_U", "Press the Touch Pad Button outside of combat to <CAQ>adjust the difficulty and your current level</C>." },
            { "PF_PS4_TIPS_13_U", "Press the Touch Pad Button during combat to <CAQ>pause the action</C>." },
            { "PF_PS4_TIPS_14_U", "Press the L1 Button outside of combat to sift through <CAQ>Rindo's thoughts</C>." },
            { "PF_PS4_TIPS_15_U", "Use the L1 or R1 Buttons to access the <CAQ>Thoughts</C> tab of the main menu, where you can explore your <CYE>Social Network</C>." },
            { "PF_PS4_TIPS_17_D", "Approach a location marked with a <CYE>Shop</C> sign and press the <PS_button_circle> Button to step inside and peruse their wares. No one store is ever the same, and each one sells a variety of unique items." },
            { "PF_PS4_TIPS_18_D", "Contactless payment via <CYE>ShibuPay</C> is the only method of monetary transfer accepted in this part of town. <CAQ>Press the △ Button</C> inside a shop to <CYE>sell extra pins</C> to boost your balance." },
            { "PF_PS4_TIPS_21_D", "Press the □ Button while <CYE>scanning</C> to activate Fret's psych, then tilt the Left Stick and Right Stick in the <CYE>correct directions</C> to reassemble the mixed-up memory." },
            { "PF_PS4_TIPS_22_D", "Press the <PS_button_circle> Button near a possessed person to <CYE>dive</C> inside their mind. Depending on your performance, you can earn <CAQ>multiple rewards</C>—so long as your difficulty is set to <CAQ>Normal or higher</C>." },
            { "PF_PS4_TIPS_23_D", "<CYE>Scan</C> to locate a portal, then approach and press the <PS_button_circle> Button to leap through it." },
            { "PF_PS4_TIPS_24_D", "<CYE>Tap the <PS_button_cross> Button in time with the music</C> to quicken your step. Soundsurfing can also <CAQ>give your Groove a boost</C> at the start of battle, so don't be afraid to feel the beat!" },
            { "PF_PS4_TIPS_26_U", "Press the □ Button when the <CYE>Replay icon</C> appears on-screen to <CAQ>activate Rindo's psych</C> and change time frames." },
            { "PF_PS4_TIPS_27_D", "<CYE>All party members, items, and stats will carry over</C> when you revisit the past, allowing you to resolve any unfinished quests and <CAQ>complete each day in its entirety</C>.<BR>To streamline your experience, press the R2 Button to <CYE>skip previously viewed cutscenes</C>." },
            { "PF_PS4_TIPS_35_D", "Hold down the <CYE>R1 Button</C> to charge up power, then release to unleash an <CYE>aerial kick</C>!" },
